(206, 2, 'Держатель настенный WM 4 0601092400 (BOSCH)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;ХАРАКТЕРИСТИКИ:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Материал: пластик&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Резьба: 5/8&quot; &quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Вес: 0,7 кг&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;ОПИСАНИЕ:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Держатель настенный BOSCH WM 4 (0601092400) обеспечивает регулировку высоты с фиксацией для точного выравнивания.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Широкая область применения благодаря принадлежностям.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Гибкий монтаж держателя.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Для GRL